        <category>Animals</category>
        <importance>2</importance>
        <availability>2</availability>
        <source>Farmer</source>

        <short>Oxen make great draft animals.</short>

        <description>
            <para>
                Oxen are castrated adult cattle commonly used as draft
                animals, either for ploughing or for pulling carts.
                Castration makes them easier to control. Until the
                horse collar reaches Europe (at the end of TL 2),
                oxen make for better draft animals than horses.
            </para>
        </description>

        <weight>750000</weight>
